title: RetroWatch Android v1.0.7
message:
RetroWatch Android v1.0.7

- Simplify UX/UI
Deleted RSS feed tab, RSS feed browser
Simplify filtering: support only 2-type filtering. One is package name
filtering and another is string-match filtering. User can select this
type by touching message item
But still user can select icon at each filter.
- Fix various bugs.
- Now battery messages and wifi messages are normal message (previously
they are emergency message)
- Remote sync interval gets longer
- Add cutom clock style in settings > clock style.

title: RetroWatch supports SPI OLEDs
message:
RetroWatch supports SPI OLEDs

Use arduino sources for SPI

title: RetroWatch supports u8glib
message:
RetroWatch supports u8glib

Updated (2015.01.12) : RetroWatch supports u8glib. Now you can use
various kind of OLED as you want and it consumes less memory. Instead
it's liitle slow at screen refresh.

title: Arduino Android v1.0.6 updates
message:
Arduino Android v1.0.6 updates

RetroWatch Android v1.0.6
- Start service again after unintended service kill
ServiceMonitoring class checks service status periodically
- Add "Run in background" menu
- Delete pre-defined RSS feed

RetroWatch Arduino v1.0.6
- Add SPI header. Many user reported that missing SPI header makes
compile error.

title: Fix SPI header error
message:
Fix SPI header error

I've reported that SPI header error occurs according to Arduino IDE.
This commit fixes SPI header error which is caused by unnecessary header
include.

title: Update RetroWatchLE for Android version under 4.3
message:
Update RetroWatchLE for Android version under 4.3

RetroWatchLE doesn't support Notification Listener Service. But runs in
Android v4.0 or over.

title: Retro Watch android v1.0
message:
Retro Watch android v1.0

Include two types of source
- Retro Watch android v1.0 is for android phone application
- only supports android v4.3 or over (To use notification service)

- Retro Watch arduino v1.0 is for your AVR board
- Especially for arduino pro mini but compatible with UNO R3 and Nano
